casebody.data:
THE UNITED STATES, PETITIONER, v. THE SUNSWICK CORPORATION, A CORPORATION OF DELAWARE [No. 46696] [109 C. Cls. 772;

334 U. S. —]

Government contract; minimum wage rate in lump sum contract increased in accordance with order of Wage Adjustment Board under Executive Order. Judgment for plaintiff.

Defendant’s petition for writ of certiorari denied by the Supreme Court May 24, 1948.
